Question: Guangzhou Kunpo Technology Development Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Guangzhou Kunpo Technology Development Co., Ltd.

Product: Lensun Screen Protector Cutting Machines and Protective Films

- Offers screen protector cutting machines and protective films certified by CE, REACH, RoHS
- Provides 25000+ protector cutting templates
- Offers warranty, technical support, service training, and operation support
- Provides protective films for various electronic devices
- Developed Oqunbo Scratch Protection technology for smart phones and mobile devices
- Offers Oqunbo Cutito, MaxO Screen Protector, and MaxO Back Skin
- Developed Lensun nano screen protectors and Dents healing full-screen film
- Released Lensun 360° full coverage protector and gained a patent
- Developed various types of screen protector cutting machines and new material types
- Innovated with dual-blade cutting mode, auto-feeding system, and new material types
- Provides retail packaging design and customization
- Open to third-party organizations for cooperation
